---
title: Creole Beef & Rainbow Veggies with Spinach Couscous & Smokey Aioli
description: Dig into an easy bowl of Creole-inspired delights! From tender and mildly spiced beef strips to rainbow veggies and wholesome
spinach couscous, this colourful meal gets a creamy dollop of smokey aioli to bring the whole flavoursome feast together, and in  only 25 minutes!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creole-beef-rainbow-veggies-8b78cd08.jpg
